  <h1 id="artTitle"><?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>Risk of prostatitis in patients with type 2 diabetes mellitus: An observational retrospective cohort study of canagliflozin versus other antihyperglycemic agents using propensity score matching</h1>

